                            "p": [
                                {
                                    "value": "Series II contains internal documents of the Workers Party and Independent Socialist League, as well as some correspondence.  These internal bulletins, minutes, reports, memos, position papers, directives, and proceedings provide good documentation of the activities, internal dynamics, and evolution of the political views of these organizations.  This series also contains correspondence to and from foreign comrades which Stewart handled at the request of the national office."
